You may fatigue equipped creature when it attacks. When you do, create a tapped and attacking token that's a copy of equipped creature except the token isn't legendary. Sacrifice the token at the beginning of the next end step. [i](To fatigue, tap it then put a stun counter on it.)[/i]
Equipped creature, and creatures you control with the same name, each get +1/+0 and have menace.
